  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>CONSTRUCTIONS INDUSTRIELLES DE LA MEDITERRANEE - CNIM SINGAPORE PRIVATE LIMITED</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will be reporting to the Project Manager as a Project Engineer (Elevator/Escalator), driving project execution and commissioning to ensure timely and successful delivery.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate and communicate effectively with customers, main contractors, sub-contractors, architects, consultants, engineers, and suppliers to ensure project milestones and commissioning are achieved successfully</li><li>Lead site meetings and perform thorough site inspections to monitor project progress and resolve issues promptly</li><li>Manage project schedules and resources to ensure smooth operations and on-time project completion</li><li>Adapt to and execute additional duties as assigned by Management to support project goals</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Electrical or Mechanical Engineering</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrated experience working on elevator/escalator projects at MRT work sites</li><li>Proven ability to manage modernization projects for escalators</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office applications including Word, Excel, and PowerPoint</li><li>Strong organizational skills to manage multiple responsibilities efficiently</li><li>Positive and proactive work attitude</li></ul>",
